description:
Prime Land – Rare Earth located within the Riverside Gardens area.

Be quick to snap up this 336sqm completely rectangle block of land situated in a cul-de-sac location surrounded by top quality homes and perfectly located for you to enjoy the Swan River, parklands and trails.

The area is great with easy access to the train station, primary schools, cafes, shops, medical suites and more.

7 Letizia is a great parcel of land and offers you the perfect opportunity to build your dream home amongst other new, quality built homes in a postcode close to everything.

Titles have been issued and the property is ready to go.

Location Highlights:
* Swan River is close by
* 10 minutes drive to the Perth CBD
* Close drive to restaurants, and shopping precinct
* FIFO workers will enjoy the close proximity to the airport
* Close drive to Swan Valley
* Easy access to a number of major road networks
* Minutes to the new Forrestfield Airport trainlink stations
* Close to Ascot Raceway
